title: King Charles urged to attend Women's World Cup in Australia
description: The boss of Australian football has urged King Charles to come to the Women's World Cup that his country is co-hosting with New Zealand.

title: Woman, 85, killed by 11ft alligator while walking dog near canal in Florida

title: Andrew Tate's detention in Romania extended for another 30 days

title: Biden says Ukraine's allies have 'iron will' as Putin suspends key nuclear treaty
description: Joe Biden has said Vladimir Putin expected his enemies to "roll over" when he invaded Ukraine but was met with the "iron will" of its allies - as the Russian president suspended a key nuclear treaty with the US after accusing the West of starting the war.

title: Putin thought his enemies would 'roll over' but he was wrong, Biden says
description: Vladimir Putin thought his enemies would "roll over" but instead he "met the will of America and nations everywhere who refused to accept a world governed by fear", Joe Biden has said.

title: Dani Alves won't be freed from prison on bail while sexual assault investigation continues

title: Japan considers raising age of consent from 13 to 16
